IMPORTANT :

Variables to exclude :
----------------------
Pay close attention when you create variables ! be creative !

As well as your prgm names,
the use of,

All the name functions into the CATALOG and system variables in the VAR-LINK menu, are to be banned as user variables name.

A pitfall to avoid :
--------------------
Avoid naming your folders with only one letter.

Ensure that incremented variables in your 'For’ Loops, are different from your folder and program names.

Furthermore, unique variables of type: alpha, are commonly used for formal computation. (Type Func for executables)

MY ADVICE :
-----------
To protect your work, calculations, and personal settings, I strongly recommend to ban the 'NewProb' from your programs.
